Problem statement
Write a recursive function that returns the sum of the digits of a given integer.

Detailed explanation ( Input/output format, Notes, Images )
Constraints :
0 <= N <= 10^9
Sample Input 1 :
12345
Sample Output 1 :
15
Sample Input 2 :
9
Sample Output 2 :
9

//code

int sumOfDigits(int n) {
    if (n < 10) 
        return n;
    return n % 10 + sumOfDigits(n / 10);
}


